        {
            "title": "登場兩新股表現迥異 傅里葉高收1倍每手賬賺4000元 銅師傅低收逾49%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">今日掛牌的兩隻新股，全日表現各走一方。半導體股傅里葉(03625)升足全日，收報80元，較招股價40元高1倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"傅里葉半導體\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/FS-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"傅里葉半導體\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/FS-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">傅里葉半導體</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">以該股1手100股計，認購並獲配每手賬面賺4000元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">相反，銅師傅(00664)則全程「潛水」，高位42元時仍較招股價60元低30%；收報30.5元，低於招股價49.17%。以1手100股計，認購並獲配每手賬面蝕2920元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15818533-%e7%99%bb%e5%a0%b4%e5%85%a9%e6%96%b0%e8%82%a1%e8%a1%a8%e7%8f%be%e8%bf%a5%e7%95%b0-%e5%82%85%e9%87%8c%e8%91%89%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b61%e5%80%8d%e6%af%8f%e6%89%8b%e8%b3%ac%e8%b3%ba4000%e5%85%83-%e9%8a%85",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/FS-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-31 16:38:45",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市︱午後整固 恒指升37點報24788點 單月挫1842點或6.92% 今年累計跌3.29%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股午後反覆整固，在3月與首季最後1個交易日以微升作結，石油與重磅科股均有份拖低大市，金融股則逆市向好。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數今早高開67點後，初段曾在內地上月官方PMI勝預期、疊加亞洲主要股市跌幅收窄的情況下，一度有上試兩萬五之勢，最高曾見24988點，升237點便乏力再上，早市中段更開始倒跌，午後初段跌幅曾擴大至191點，低見24559點，其後重新進入反覆整固局面。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指最後收報24788點，升37點或0.15%；總結3月份則跌1842點或6.92%；年初至今累計則跌842點或3.29%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅科股今日是拖低大市的主力之一，恒生科技指數全日均跑輸，收跌40點或0.86%，報4649點；國企指數跌24點或0.3%，報8374點。主板成交2557.6億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15818500-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e6%95%b4%e5%9b%ba-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8737%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b124788%e9%bb%9e-%e5%96%ae%e6%9c%88%e6%8c%ab1842%e9%bb%9e%e6%88%966-92",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-5.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-31 16:26:38",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股午後見全日低  深股跌逾1.8%  3 月滬股跌逾6%深股跌逾7%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股午後再跌，滬股跌破3900，深股跌破13500，創業板指數跌2.36%，兩市成交19925.43億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-8.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-8.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指全日報3891，跌31點或0.8%，今早以3924點開市，升不足1點或0.02%，早段高見3948點，升25點或0.64%，中段反覆向下，午後跌破上午低位，跌破3900關，見3892，跌31點或0.79%，全日成交8919.45億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬股3 月全月跌271點或6.51%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指全日報13478，跌248點或1.81%，今早開市報13683點，則跌42點或0.31%。中段見13783，升57點或0.42%，為全日高位，即拾級而下，午後趺破上午低位，最多挫240點或1.75%，報13486，全日成交11005.98億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深股3月累計跌1017點或7.02%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數全日跌25點0.58%，報4465點，今早開跌不足1點，開報4491點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數全日跌77點或2.36%，報3196點，今早開市報3247點，跌26點或0.8%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15818047-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e8%a6%8b%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e4%bd%8e-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be1-8-3-%e6%9c%88%e6%bb%ac%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be6%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-9.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-31 16:20:03",
